  "notes": "HAR-675 captured live Shopify Admin GraphQL 2026-04 behavior for deleting a disposable metaobject definition with two associated entries. Shopify returned the deleted definition GID with no userErrors, and immediate downstream reads by definition id, type, metaobject id, metaobject handle, and type catalog all returned null or empty connection results. The fixture also includes a MetaobjectDefinitionHydrateByType cassette entry for cold create-path hydration; the delete step itself must not call upstream at runtime."
